ea had recalled their player.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998864766504, \"rank\": 1.1019047088409839e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9981989142738583, \"rank\": 0.0009098540232380193, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Football_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Football Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Football_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Football_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.59486957282097e-17, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Lesley Ugochukwu leaves the Olympic selection,' a statement read.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesley_Ugochukwu\", \"score\": 0.9999995508322727, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lesley Ugochukwu\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesley_Ugochukwu\", \"dbped