rce/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6140053145706605, \"rank\": 0.4755844269855226, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The technical staff, who have made a request to the organisers to be able to replace him, are awaiting a response.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The current group is therefore made up of twenty-one players.'\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a non-FIFA competition, clubs are under no obligation to let their players compete at the Olympics, withChelsea already blocking Malo Gusto and Benoit Badiashilefrom being called up by Henry.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malo_Gusto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malo Gusto\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malo_Gusto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malo_Gusto\"}, {\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Benoit\", \"score\": 0.83762695650023, \"rank\": 0.19377442077956966, \"text\": \"Benoit\", \"t